name: StormMan-son
description:
StormMan -son
Those superstars with messy clothing, disorderly lifestyle, and abnormal behavior eventually appear as persons who are very concerned about serious issues and essential human values. Through song lyrics and personal statements they comment on freedom, eternity, politics and economy, existential loneliness, godliness, and others. In the painting called “The Notorious Bogeyman (Marilyn Manson)” the words of the brutal and satanic rock star Marilyn Manson have strong spiritual vibes. His statements “I believe I am God” sounds similar with the controversial statement uttered by Al-Hallaj.
